item.description:
UPDATE: It looks like the phone banks are not installed yet - please bring a cell phone if you have one. There will still be work to do in any case stuffing envelopes.

Come join us in the new campaign headquarters for some phone banking of current supporters to get them to come to the 3 Nov event. It's low pressure as these are current supporters, and we'll enjoy some pizza while we do it. We will go from 6:30pm to 8:30pm
item.name: Phone Banking
